 1993-Nov. 1995>.", "Includes news for surrounding areas: Hampton, Phoebus, Old Point, Williamsburg, etc.", "Includes supplements; a combined supplement for the Daily Press and the Times-herald (Newport News, Va.) was included in July, 1956; and on Oct. 18, 1981.", "Archived issues are available in digital format as part of the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection.", "In 1913 publisher of Daily press combined with publisher of Times-herald and published morning eds. called: Daily press; evening eds. called: Times-herald.", "A joint Sat. ed. of the Times-herald and Daily press was published from <1984>-Aug. 4, 1990.", "In 1991 the Times-herald (Newport News, Va. : 1905) was absorbed by the Daily press (Newport News, Va. : Final ed.).", "Description based on: Mar. 24, 1898.", "Latest issue consulted: May 6, 2001."], "number": ["sn83045830", "1", "00175031303"], "number_edition": ["1"], "number_lccn": ["sn83045830"], "number_reel": ["00175031303"], "numeric_shelf_id": 190710131, "online_format": ["image", "pdf", "online text"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_formats": [{"label": "MODSXML Record", "link": "//tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/ndnp//vi/batch_vi_capri_ver01/data/sn83045830/00175031303/1907101301/1907101301_1.xml"}, {"label": "MARCXML Record", "link": "//lccn.loc.gov/sn83045830/marcxml"}], "partof": [{"count": 2163, "title": "daily press (newport news, va.) 1896-current", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=partof:daily+press+%28newport+news,+va.%29+1896-current&fo=json"}, {"count": 3203926, "title": "chronicling america", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/chronicling-america/?fo=json"}, {"count": 3225157, "title": "serial and government publications division", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=partof:serial+and+government+publications+division&fo=json"}], "partof_collection": ["chronicling america"], "partof_division": ["serial and government publications division"], "partof_title": ["daily press (newport news, va.) 1896-current"], "place_of_publication": "Newport News, Va.", "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "raw_lccn": "sn 83045830 ", "reel_numbers": ["00175031303"], "resources": [{"files": 14, "image": "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:vi:batch_vi_capri_ver01:data:sn83045830:00175031303:1907101301:0875/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83045830/1907-10-13/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}], "rights": ["<p>The Library of Congress believes that the newspapers in Chronicling America are in the public domain or have no known copyright restrictions.  Newspapers published in the United States more than 95 years ago are in the public domain in their entirety. Any newspapers in Chronicling America that were published less than 95 years ago are also believed to be in the public domain, but may contain some copyrighted third party materials. Researchers using newspapers published less than 95 years ago should be alert for modern content (for example, registered and renewed for copyright and published with notice) that may be copyrighted.  Responsibility for making an independent legal assessment of an item and securing any necessary permissions ultimately rests with persons desiring to use the item.</p>\n<p>The NEH awardee responsible for producing each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.017402, "shard": "02", "shelf_id": "sn83045830, 1907-10-13, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/vi", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["virginia", "newport news", "hampton (va.)", "hampton", "newspapers", "newport news (va.)", "united states"], "subject_headings": ["Newport News (Va.)--Newspapers", "Hampton (Va.)--Newspapers", "Virginia--Hampton", "Virginia--Newport News", "United States--Virginia--Newport News"], "subjects": [{"hampton": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:hampton&fo=json"}, {"hampton (va.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:hampton+%28va.%29&fo=json"}, {"newport news": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newport+news&fo=json"}, {"newport news (va.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newport+news+%28va.%29&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}, {"virginia": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:virginia&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2024-02-06T19:59:51.872Z", "title": "Daily press (Newport News, Va.), October 13, 1907", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn83045830/1907-10-13/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn83045830/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn83045830", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/59102307-f656-5adc-8744-5564a3bf154c"], "batch": ["vi_aqua_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1896", "description": ["Daily Began 1896. Cf. Cappon, L.J. Va. newspapers. Editor: C.E. Thacker, <1898>. \"Extra\" supplements were published as part of the Final ed. <Jan. 1993-Nov. 1995>. Includes news for surrounding areas: Hampton, Phoebus, Old Point, Williamsburg, etc. Includes supplements; a combined supplement for the Daily Press and the Times-herald (Newport News, Va.) was included in July, 1956; and on Oct. 18, 1981. Archived issues are available in digital format as part of the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. In 1913 publisher of Daily press combined with publisher of Times-herald and published morning eds. called: Daily press; evening eds. called: Times-herald. A joint Sat. ed. of the Times-herald and Daily press was published from <1984>-Aug. 4, 1990. In 1991 the Times-herald (Newport News, Va. : 1905) was absorbed by the Daily press (Newport News, Va. : Final ed.). Description based on: Mar. 24, 1898. Latest issue consulted: May 6, 2001."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:09.423Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-00", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-00"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn83045830/", "image_url": [], "index": 10, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [36.977714, -76.430349], "location": ["virginia", "newport news", "united states", "hampton"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-76.430349, 36.977714], "number": ["7529015", "microfilm service copy", "sn97066024", "univ of virginia", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn83045830/1898-01-11/ed-1/", "2163-7156", "sn97066022", "sn83045830", "sn91066051", "2025-07-29t10:49:55.500000", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "1", "college of william & mary", "library of virginia, the", "sn97066023", "2162", "franklin d roosevelt libr", "arkansas state univ - jonesboro", "2024-01-28t09:26:30.871975", "virginia historical society library", "online resource", "original", "center for res libr, newsp proj", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn83045830/1910-12-22/ed-1/"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "daily press (newport news, va.) 1896-current", "serial and government publications division", "catalog", "chronicling america"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 68.02485, "shelf_id": "Newspaper F234.N5 D34", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["virginia", "newport news", "hampton (va.)", "hampton", "newspapers", "newport news (va.)", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-07-18T09:07:48.184Z", "title": "Daily press", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn83045830/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2021220197/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1896", "dates": ["[1896 TO 9999]"], "description": ["Daily Print began in 1896. Editor: C.E. Thacker, <1898>. \"Extra\" supplements were published as part of the Final ed. <Jan. 1993-Nov. 1995>. Includes news for surrounding areas: Hampton, Phoebus, Old Point, Williamsburg, etc. Includes supplements; a combined supplement for the Daily Press and the Times-herald (Newport News, Va.) was included in July, 1956; and on Oct. 18, 1981. In 1913 publisher of Daily press combined with publisher of Times-herald and published morning eds. called: Daily press; evening eds. called: Times-herald. A joint Sat. ed. of the Times-herald and Daily press was published from <1984>-Aug. 4, 1990. In 1991 the Times-herald (Newport News, Va. : 1905) was absorbed by the Daily press (Newport News, Va. : Final ed.). Vol. III, No. 7 (January 11, 1898); title from caption (Chronicling America's website, viewed Mar. 15, 2021). March 15, 2021 (Newspaper home page, viewed Mar. 15, 2021)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:12.813Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2021220197/", "image_url": [], "index": 11, "language": ["english"], "location": ["virginia", "newport news", "united states", "hampton"], "number": ["online resource", "2767-5971", "sn91066051", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2021220197", "681734666"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "daily press (newport news, va;newport news, virginia) 1896-current [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 58.910664, "shelf_id": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/c